    Gorg = Blade("Gorg", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/c/c3/XC2-element-water.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030959", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/2/2d/XC2_Gorg_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040029", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/9/9b/XC2_Greataxe_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230247", "He possesses a strong work ethic and works to be a reliable Blade for his Driver. He does possess a weakness for sweets, having a great desire to own a Patisserie if he were ever given leave from his regular duties as a Blade, and can even become distracted in conversation if a nearby dessert catches his eye.")
    Boreas = Blade("Boreas", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/d/d0/XC2-element-wind.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030959", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/5/5a/XC2_Boreas_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040018", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f7/XC2_Bitball_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230240", "Boreas is childlike in mannerism and loves to eat, to the point where he will lick party members to see if they taste good. He is easily upset if anything prevents him from eating and has the unique ability to travel as fast as the wind, which he uses sometimes accidentally if he loses his temper.")
    Dagas = Blade("Dagas", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/4/4e/XC2-element-fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030957", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/5/57/XC2_Dagas_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040019", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/9/9b/XC2_Greataxe_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230247", "Dagas is extremely haughty and arrogant. He is convinced he is the ruler of a nation, despite Blades having no memories of their previous lives, and rationalizes his status as a Blade as a necessary burden to maintain his rule. As such, he is quick to anger at the slightest perceived disrespect and expects to be treated with reverence.")
    Kasandra = Blade("Kasandra", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/3/3c/XC2-element-dark.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030955", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/nintendo/images/a/a5/Kasandra_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20181001005314&path-prefix=en", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/0/0c/XC2_Shield_Hammer_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230346", "Kasandra comes across as a very cheery young Blade, though the mask on the back of her head radiates with a dark aura. Additionally, during some specials, the mask covers her face and upon coming off, Kasandra acts as if she had no idea what happened. Kasandra considers herself very lucky, making her very unaware of the misfortune she brings to people around her.")
    Praxis = Blade("Praxis", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/c/c3/XC2-element-water.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030959", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/c/c0/XC2_Praxis_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040053", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/5/58/XC2_Megalance_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230250", "Praxis is shown to be kind, if a bit sassy. She becomes very friendly and supportive in behavior. She is horrified to learn that she was a criminal in her previous life.")
    Theory = Blade("Theory", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/1/1c/XC2-element-ice.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030958", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/0/07/XC2_Theory_Artwork.png/revision/latest/top-crop/width/300/height/300?cb=20190203040101", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/3/3a/XC2_Chroma_Katana_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230243", "Theory is quite cold toward others, including her Driver.")
    Perun = Blade("Perun", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/1/1c/XC2-element-ice.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030958", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/fa/Perun_Portrait.png/revision/latest/top-crop/width/360/height/450?cb=20200424074154", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/5/58/XC2_Megalance_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230250", "Perun is a valiant warrior, fighting relentlessly to help others. She dedicates her very existence to justice and will fight to her last breath to protect others, and will loyally follow the party who shares this sense. She is sensitive to the needs of others and will hold back if fighting all out can lead to innocent people being hurt or killed.")
    Kora = Blade("Kora", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/b/b1/XC2-element-electric.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030957", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/4/4d/XC2_Kora_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040041", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f9/XC2_Knuckle_Claws_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230249", "Kora is chatty and emotive, loving gossip and being trendy. She is easily excited and will often talk excessively and seems thoughtless toward others.")
    Azami = Blade("Azami", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/3/3c/XC2-element-dark.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030955", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/0/0c/XC2_Azami_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040018", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/a/ac/XC2_Ether_Cannon_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230247", "Azami can be very possessive of her Driver. She will take rather extreme action if she senses anything suspicious.")
    Ursula = Blade("Ursula", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/1/1c/XC2-element-ice.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030958", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/8/88/XC2_Ursula_Artwork.png/revision/latest/top-crop/width/300/height/300?cb=20190203040101", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f9/XC2_Knuckle_Claws_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230249", "Ursula is a very kindhearted yet soft-spoken Blade always accompanied by Beary. She enjoys singing a great deal. However, she is incredibly shy and has great difficulty bringing herself to meet new people, much less sing in front of an audience.")
    Newt = Blade("Newt", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/4/4e/XC2-element-fire.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030957", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/4/44/XC2_Newt_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040042", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/3/3a/XC2_Chroma_Katana_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230243", "Newt loves to fight and is incredibly excited about Titan weapons and the army of the Empire of Mor Ardain.")
    Nim = Blade("Nim", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/2/26/XC2-element-earth.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030956", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/9/9e/XC2_Nim_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040043", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f9/XC2_Knuckle_Claws_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230249", "Nim is a cheery young woman driven by her love of nature, which she reveres above all else.")
    Sheba = Blade("Sheba", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/c/c3/XC2-element-water.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030959", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/0/03/XC2_Sheba_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040101", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/a/ac/XC2_Ether_Cannon_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230247", "Sheba is an extravagant Blade, having a taste for luxury and expensive items. She desires nothing more than to form an entourage of women, and so looks down on men as a means to her ends. She does not appear to be easily discouraged from her goal.")
    Vess = Blade("Vess", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/b/b1/XC2-element-electric.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030957", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/nintendo/images/9/90/Xenoblade_Chronicles_2_-_Vess.png/revision/latest?cb=20171110172833&path-prefix=en", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f7/XC2_Bitball_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230240", "Vess has a very nurturing, motherly personality, providing a meaningful mother figure to her previous Driver's children and expressing a substantial desire to cook for and heal those around her. She is gentle, docile, and well-liked.")
    Adenine = Blade("Adenine", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/d/d0/XC2-element-wind.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030959", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f7/XC2_Adenine_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040017", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/f/f9/XC2_Knuckle_Claws_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230249", "Adenine is a scholar, interested in learning and books. She speaks using a wide range of vocabulary. Additionally, she is excited at the prospect of new knowledge; the Tomes of Morytha in particular.")
    Electra = Blade("Electra", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/b/b1/XC2-element-electric.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030957", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/5/59/XC2_Electra_Artwork.png/revision/latest?cb=20190203040028", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/0/0c/XC2_Shield_Hammer_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230346", "Her best quality is perhaps her cheery, energizing personality. However, Electra is easily upset and desires to be more directly helpful.")
    Zenobia = Blade("Zenobia", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/d/d0/XC2-element-wind.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/36?cb=20180425030959", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/nintendo/images/8/8c/Xenoblade_Chronicles_2_-_Zenobia.png/revision/latest?cb=20171110171128&path-prefix=en", "https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/xenoblade/images/9/9b/XC2_Greataxe_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/40?cb=20190405230247", "While generally well meaning in what she does, Zenobia also has an incredible lust for battle and constantly seeks stronger and stronger opponents to fight.")
